Package views

Class Summary
AudioRecorderActivity This class will act as the activity where the user can record audio on the fly for task submissions.
CreateTaskActivity This class is an activity where the user will enter relevant information for creating a new class.
EditTaskActivity This class is an activity which allows the author of a task to edit relevant information
    Task Name Task Description Task Requirements: Audio, Photo, Text Task Scope: Public/Private Any submissions submitted to the task may be deleted Delete the entire task
FulfillTaskActivity This class is an activity which allows the user to perform the actions requested by a task author.
MainActivity This is the activity that is called when the app is first launched.
MainScreenActivity This is the main screen of the app.
MemoryCheckActivity This class handles checking for images or audio files in the device's memory, for the ability to attach pre-existing media to a fulfillment.
PhotoTakerActivity This class handles the taking of photos on-the-fly for task fulfillment submissions.
ViewResponseActivity This class is an activity that allows a user to view a fulfillment selected from ViewTaskActivity.
ViewTaskActivity This class is an activity that allows a user to view a task before they decide to fulfill it.
